The Cartographer's geographic archive holds an outdated floor plan of the Gloamvault of Kel'Shadra that predates the vault's current access configuration. The survey record needs a full update before the reference collection can be issued to expedition planners. Enter the vault and chart every traversable chamber so the archive can publish an accurate current-edition document.
